description:
Today on the podcast, we hear from Dara Taylor, the Composer of Marvel Television’s Ironheart, and the show’s Music Supervisor, Dave Jordan. Plus, we revisit our favorite sci-fi science moments from the MCU and are joined by LEGO’s Jesper Nielsen and Disney’s Jesse Falcon to chat about the latest LEGO Marvel Brickverse!
